										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Hello, lovelies!  I have something new and shiny for you.  Feast your eyes on the brand new cover for <a href="http://clockworktwist.com/missing/">Clockwork Twist : Missing</a>, the forth book in the series!</p>
<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2732" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Front02-mid.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="1000" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Front02-mid.jpg 640w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Front02-mid-192x300.jpg 192w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/Front02-mid-618x965.jpg 618w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></p>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-2739" src="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Missing-cover-sm.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="575" srcset="http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Missing-cover-sm.jpg 800w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Missing-cover-sm-300x215.jpg 300w, http://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/Missing-cover-sm-618x444.jpg 618w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p>Now, you might be wondering, why does the cover look like a view from orbit?  Well, you&#8217;d better go and read the description right <a title="Book Four: Missing" href="http://clockworktwist.com/missing/">here</a>.</p>
<p>Want more than that?  Well, the first 3 chapters will appear right here on clockworktwist.com, starting on the 12th.</p>
<p>You STILL want more??  Greedy&#8230;  I guess there&#8217;s nothing for it.  You&#8217;re simply going to have to go reserve your eBook pre-order, right now.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/dp/B017S0NK8I" target="_blank"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="http://i1.wp.com/media.corporate-ir.net/media_files/irol/17/176060/KindleLogos/Kindlelogo/scr2555-proj697-a-kindle-logo-rgb-lg.jpg?resize=148%2C40" alt="" width="148" height="40" /></a></p>
<p><a href="https://www.smashwords.com/books/view/591722" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://dwtr67e3ikfml.cloudfront.net/static/1/swlogo.png" alt="" width="160" height="43" /></a></p>
<p>Mind you, only the eBooks are pre-order-able at the moment, but the paperback is in final review and will also be coming soon.  If the stars align, it will be available on the 17th, just in time for Twist&#8217;s birthday.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
